title: The Robot vs. The Aztec Mummy (La Momia Azteca Contro El Robot Humano) 1958 - English

sources.title: The Robot vs. The Aztec Mummy (La Momia Azteca Contro El Robot Humano) 1958 - English
sources.description: The walking Aztec mummy Popoca has returned, and this time he is pitted against a mad scientist and his creation, the Human Robot, a cyborg with a mechanical body, steel claws and a human head!!! This film is known to be sold by distributors that deal exclusively in public domain properties.
